Hey, this is Moe S.
from the Mattress King.

20:49.181 --> 20:51.918
Give me a call at 555-0146.

20:51.951 --> 20:53.653
For a limited time only,

20:53.686 --> 20:56.956
the Mattress King's got
queen mattress sets for $99

20:56.989 --> 20:59.459
and king sets for $129.

21:01.428 --> 21:03.262
HOMER:
Ooh! Are you okay?

21:03.296 --> 21:06.265
Oh, yeah. I'm fine.

21:06.299 --> 21:08.100
That's what I was afraid
was gonna... (grunts)

21:08.134 --> 21:09.769
that's what I was
afraid was gonna happen

21:09.802 --> 21:11.671
-with that damn thing.
-You all right?

21:11.704 --> 21:13.172
-Oh, I'm fine.
-You sure?

21:13.205 --> 21:15.174
Messed up my guitar, though.
No, I'm fine.

21:15.207 --> 21:16.676
-You sure you're, uh...
-No, I'm fine.

21:16.709 --> 21:18.010
Try your arm and stuff.

21:18.044 --> 21:19.746
-He's wearing leather.
-Oh, okay.

21:19.779 --> 21:21.614
-Did you get it on film?
-Yeah.

21:21.648 --> 21:23.550
All right. All right!

21:25.485 --> 21:27.153
Shh!
